{"id": "art-171", "label": "Art. 171", "title": "Art. 171", "slug": "art-171", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 171 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)<span\nclass=SpellE>De&#355;in&#259;torii</span> de <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iuni</span>\nse pot întruni în adunare general&#259;, pentru a delibera asupra intereselor\nlor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Adunarea va fi convocat&#259; pe\ncheltuiala <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> care a emis <span\nclass=SpellE>obliga&#355;iunile</span>, la cererea unui num&#259;r de <span\nclass=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;tori</span> care s&#259; reprezinte a patra parte\ndin titlurile emise <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> nerambursate sau,\ndup&#259; numirea <span class=SpellE>reprezentan&#355;ilor</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;torilor</span> de <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iuni</span>,\nla cererea acestora.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)<span class=SpellE>Dispozi&#355;iile</span>\nprev&#259;zute pentru adunarea ordinar&#259; a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>\nse aplic&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> adun&#259;rii <span\nclass=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;torilor</span> de <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iuni</span>,\nîn ce <span class=SpellE>prive&#351;te</span> formele, <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span>,\ntermenele convoc&#259;rii, depunerea titlurilor <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nvotarea.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(4)Societatea emitent&#259; nu poate\nparticipa la deliber&#259;rile adun&#259;rii <span class=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;torilor</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iuni</span>, în baza <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iunilor</span>\npe care le posed&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_455023611\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1991\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_455023611\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)<span class=SpellE>De&#355;in&#259;torii</span> de <span\nclass=SpellE>obliga&#355;iuni</span> vor putea fi <span class=SpellE>reprezenta&#355;i</span>\nprin mandatari, <span class=SpellE>al&#355;ii</span> decât administratorii,\ndirectorii, respectiv membrii directoratului, ai consiliului de supraveghere\nori cenzorii sau <span class=SpellE>func&#355;ionarii</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}